text:
Thank you for your hard work!
That concludes the shoot────!
Thank you, and great job everyone!

Good job.
Next up is the interview.

Alright.
──Oh, should I change out of this costume?

Well, since we'll be using the photos we
just took, you can change if you want.

If you want to take your time, you can stay as you are──
Whatever's most comfortable for you, Yuika.
I see, then I might quickly change.

P-tan, you'll have to wait outside
during that time...

Oh, please don't worry about me.
I can't have you conducting the interview by yourself.
